622
00:34:52,599 --> 00:34:53,400
How can you be sure
the one you love

623
00:34:54,199 --> 00:34:55,320
is worth it?

624
00:34:58,440 --> 00:34:59,320
Actually, I do know
someone like that.

625
00:35:00,039 --> 00:35:01,039
If you love her,

626
00:35:01,639 --> 00:35:02,440
