627
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:03,880
Who?

628
00:35:06,119 --> 00:35:06,960
Yourself.

629
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,079
[I should be the one apologizing.]

630
00:35:14,039 --> 00:35:15,440
[Maybe I've been stubborn,]

631
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:16,719
[causing you misunderstanding,]

632
00:35:16,719 --> 00:35:18,280
[and giving you trouble. Sorry.]

633
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:19,920
[It won't happen again.]

634
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:52,679
You forgot something?

635
00:35:53,599 --> 00:35:54,320
No, I didn't.

636
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:00,199
Then why are you back?

637
00:36:00,639 --> 00:36:01,599
Can't I come back?

638
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:03,400
You can.

639
00:36:05,519 --> 00:36:06,960
Suddenly remembered my bulb

640
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:07,960
