641
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,559
It's about time.

642
00:36:39,599 --> 00:36:40,360
Let's call it a day.

643
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:42,840
I'll take you back

644
00:36:43,199 --> 00:36:44,559
and grab something from the firm.

645
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:45,880
Okay.

646
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,079
Off work.

647
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,599
Off work.

648
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:57,679
Let me help you.

649
00:37:01,719 --> 00:37:02,360
When you go up,
talk to her nicely.

650
00:37:03,199 --> 00:37:04,159
Don't fight.

651
00:37:04,519 --> 00:37:05,159
Got it, got it.

652
00:37:06,519 --> 00:37:07,280
Hello, Mr. Xu.
Hello.

653
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:20,599
Excuse me,

654
00:37:20,599 --> 00:37:21,639
could you press 1 for us?

655
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:22,239
Sure.
Okay.

656
00:37:24,159 --> 00:37:24,840
