657
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,280
Hi, Miss Sun.

658
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,920
Why is it stuck on the 8th floor?

659
00:37:52,519 --> 00:37:53,280
Let me check.

660
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:01,360
What's happening?

661
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:05,760
Stand in the corner.

662
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:06,920
Lower your center of gravity.

663
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,679
Hold the handrail.

664
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,559
Help!

665
00:38:26,679 --> 00:38:28,119
Oh my god!

666
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:31,679
Are you okay?

667
00:38:35,039 --> 00:38:36,559
Don't worry, I'm here.

668
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:39,159
What do I do? I...

669
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:41,440
I haven't found a job yet,

670
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:43,320
I don't have a boyfriend,

671
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,519
I've never even held a guy's hand,

672
00:38:45,519 --> 00:38:46,920
