673
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,440
And now I'm going to die.

674
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:53,320
I'll die as a third wheel.

675
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:54,679
Hey,

676
00:38:57,599 --> 00:38:58,719
