677
00:39:00,199 --> 00:39:02,119
I don't have a boyfriend either.

678
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,519
I'm already 28.

679
00:39:04,159 --> 00:39:05,119
Don't be scared.

680
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:08,920
Really?

681
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:14,679
But at least you have someone.

682
00:39:33,039 --> 00:39:34,599
Are you all okay?

683
00:39:34,639 --> 00:39:35,079
We're fine.
Please check on this lady.

684
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:37,280
Okay, okay.

685
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,440
Are you okay?

686
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,519
That scared me.

687
00:39:40,519 --> 00:39:41,319
So sorry,
I'm so sorry,

688
00:39:42,199 --> 00:39:42,840
- That scared me.
- Alright,
please check it again.

689
00:39:43,760 --> 00:39:45,000
Okay, I'll check it now.

690
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,239
- I'll check it now.
- Scared me.

691
00:39:48,639 --> 00:39:49,480
