692
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,800
My lost soul.

693
00:39:55,239 --> 00:39:57,360
I forgot I have an audition.

694
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:59,239
Your makeup is smeared.

695
00:40:06,440 --> 00:40:07,159
Ruan Yu.

696
00:40:10,840 --> 00:40:11,679
Do you want one?

697
00:40:13,559 --> 00:40:14,280
Want what?

698
00:40:17,519 --> 00:40:18,239
Never mind.

699
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:20,719
I'll go get the car.

700
00:40:39,679 --> 00:40:40,360
Ruan Yu.

701
00:40:42,639 --> 00:40:43,480
Do you want one?

702
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:51,559
Does he mean it that way?

703
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,360
Why only say half?

704
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:21,480
Tell me.

705
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,679
[When a man asks a woman,]

706
00:41:24,119 --> 00:41:25,679
["Do you want a boyfriend?"]

707
00:41:26,199 --> 00:41:27,440
[does he,]

708
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:28,360
[actually mean]

709
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:29,840
["What do you think of me?"]

710
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,840
What else?
Otherwise, is he trying

711
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,679
to set you up with someone else?

712
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:34,800
Do you even need to ask?

713
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,400
But I didn't get it at the time.

714
00:41:36,639 --> 00:41:37,280
[Will he think]
[I was pretending?]

715
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:39,119
[And just drop it?]

716
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,719
If you don't want it dropped,

717
00:41:41,719 --> 00:41:43,039
