766
00:44:14,119 --> 00:44:14,840
She fell asleep.

767
00:44:34,239 --> 00:44:35,280
It seems like the homeroom teacher coming.

768
00:44:38,280 --> 00:44:39,000
I lost.

769
00:44:39,559 --> 00:44:40,079
Lost.
What?

770
00:44:43,559 --> 00:44:44,239
Um,

771
00:44:47,519 --> 00:44:48,960
the second last line,

772
00:44:48,960 --> 00:44:50,000
I missed a minus sign.

773
00:44:50,079 --> 00:44:50,599
I miscalculated.

774
00:44:51,880 --> 00:44:52,679
See, I told you.

775
00:44:52,679 --> 00:44:53,800
I definitely got it right.

776
00:44:54,280 --> 00:44:56,000
Scared of the teacher's scolding?

777
00:44:57,679 --> 00:44:59,199
Don't forget, three orders of fried chicken.

778
00:45:00,920 --> 00:45:02,599
Next time, go home with your mom.

779
00:45:03,440 --> 00:45:04,880
She has fewer students for questions.

780
00:45:05,719 --> 00:45:06,719
One problem here

781
00:45:06,880 --> 00:45:07,920
