782
00:45:08,320 --> 00:45:09,039
No fixed time.

783
00:45:13,440 --> 00:45:14,480
[Three orders of fried chicken]

784
00:45:14,559 --> 00:45:15,920
[to get her home earlier.]

785
00:45:16,519 --> 00:45:17,119
[Not a bad deal.]

786
00:45:20,400 --> 00:45:22,159
Baby, say more sweet...

787
00:45:22,159 --> 00:45:23,280
Good morning.

788
00:45:23,280 --> 00:45:24,119
Have breakfast?

789
00:45:24,280 --> 00:45:25,239
